title: Not Hesitation Marks
description:
There was a "leak" of the Nine Inch Nails album "Hesitation Marks" on YouTube recently.  It was taken down fairly quickly.  The only Nine Inch Nails song on it was the already released Came Back Haunted.  The rest I didn't recognize.  But it wasn't Nine Inch Nails.  Some of it wasn't even very good.  But for the sake of clarity - it was not Hesitation Marks.

It was a full, single track.  I cut it up and put a better copy of Came Back Haunted where it was on the "album."  The rest I just titled not  based on the Hesitation Marks track list.  So, yes, only one track on the "leak" was actually NIN.

...Enjoy?
